summary: Moments from Codename Villanelle: No Tomorrow that I would happily trade my left tit to see worked into season 2 of Killing...
body:
Moments from Codename Villanelle: No Tomorrow that I would happily trade my left tit to see worked into season 2 of Killing Eve

- After turning down sex with Niko, Eve rubs one out while thinking about Villanelle before realizing he’s still awake and 100% watching her.

- Villanelle disguised as a crusty gutter punk solves the crossword clue “a death of crows” for a random couple on the train before dipping out.

- Villanelle, soaking in the tub with nothing but a pair of rubber gloves on, coerces Eve into washing her hair.

- Eve and Villanelle run away together !!!
